data.description: Cute no HOA concrete block home with attractive Stone exterior finish. This home features large ceramic tile throughout and beautiful honey colored cabinets in the kitchen. Kitchen countertops with a natural stone appearance. This home also features energy saving ceiling fans throughout and window sunscreens for heat protection.A new roof was just installed October 2023, this home is close to South Mountain Community Community college, shopping, freeways and downtown Phoenix.
